result.formatted_address: 1 Wu Kwong St, Hung Hom, Hong Kong
result.name: Zan Hao Taiwan Cuisine

reviews.text:
Newly renovated to include the neighbouring shop space.  Same tasty food, now brighter and larger.
Still fills up quickly at lunchtime, so it's best to go early when open for business.
Marinated pork rice is very good, as is the braised beef noodles with very tender well stewed beef.

Quite crowded though, food with good quality for the price and I especially like the 鹵水大腸. Bubble milk tea not too sweet as those chain store but the tea wasn't strong enough. Somewhere worth to visit again.
Real Taiwanese food. I love the salted fried chicken and the Taiwanese sausage. Food was nice. Atmosphere was warm (even better after the renovation). Price was reasonable. Highly recommended.

One of our go to dinner places in Hung Hom. Food is great and the new renovated place looks modern. This place is packed and better be prepared to wait in line. Alternatively, take out is a good option.
The food are great, I would definitely visit again but the drink are not recommend to get any of them.

result.adr_address: 香港紅磡湖光街1號
result.name: 讚好台灣

reviews.text:
算抵食的台式下午茶

平時見晚餐時段間唔中都要排隊，見今日下午茶時段唔使排隊，可以試吓。個下午茶餐牌唔係主動攞出嚟㗎，要問先至攞出黎。

$34元包一款主食，三款小食及一杯飲品，都算幾多選擇；

肉燥湯麵分量似台灣夜市牛肉麵嘅份量，面底普通，湯冇乜味；

鹽酥雞揸得唔錯幾脆口；

台式香腸及台式滷蛋水準合格；

肉操飯嘅份量都算多，食量少嘅人已經可以當晚飯食；

木魚炸豆腐個豆腐都幾滑。

椒麻牛肚絲都幾\，有四川嘅麻辣程度。

台式奶茶嗌左少甜， 感覺味道怪怪地，啊仔個杯正常甜嘅味道亦都係一個正常嘅珍珠奶茶。

成個下午茶餐牌，同零一間台式嘅X牛餐廳差唔多，價錢亦差唔多，唔知係咪同一個集團呢。一句講晒下午茶都算抵食。

Newly renovated to include the neighbouring shop space.  Same tasty food, now brighter and larger.
Still fills up quickly at lunchtime, so it's best to go early when open for business.
Marinated pork rice is very good, as is the braised beef noodles with very tender well stewed beef.
抵食下午茶，食物質數高！
好食既，但食得多回就欠新意了，建議多些選擇

讚好台灣的食物的確有種台灣味。試了牛肉面和魯肉飯都是第一次到訪的必食之選，一次過可以食到最台灣的風味。

唯一不足的是舖面和住座就完全香港化，非常窄而且不舒服。跟台灣有很大差別。對比同樣是食台菜的鐵牛比較，「鐵牛」環境和座位就好多很多。

價錢訂價較「鐵牛」平，大約四十至六十蚊一個主食。
